<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">والكَنْخَبة:</span> اخْتِلَاط الْكَلَام من الخطَأ، حَكَاهُ يُونُس.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>والبُخنك، لُغَة فِي <span class="c1">" البُخنق "</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>الْخَاء وَالْجِيم<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">الخَيْسَفُوج:</span> حبُّ القُطن.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">والخَيْسَفُوج:</span> العُشَرُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">وَقيل:</span> هُوَ نْبت يَتقصف ويَتثنىّ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">والخَيْسَفُوج:</span> حَبْل الشِّراع.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">وَقيل:</span> هُوَ الشّراع نَفسه.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">والخَيْسَفُوجة:</span> موضعٌ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">والخَزْرَجُ:</span> الرِّيحُ الجَنُوب.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">وَقيل:</span> هِيَ الرّيح الْبَارِدَة،<span class="c5"> قَالَ أَبُو ذُؤَيْب:</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>عَذَوْن عُجالَى وانْتَحتْهنّ خَزْرُجٌ مُقَفِّيةٌ آثارهنّ هَدُوجُ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c5">وَقيل:</span> هِيَ الشَّديدة.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c5">والخَزْرجُ:</span> اسْم رَجُلٍ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c5">وخنزج:</span> تكّبر.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c5">ورجُلٌ خَنْزَجٌ:</span> ضَخم.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>والخَدَلَّجّة،<span class="c5"> من النِّسَاء:</span> الريَّاء الممتلئة.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span class="c5">وَقيل:</span> هِيَ الضَّخمة السَّاقَيْن،<span class="c5"> والذّكَر:</span> خَدَلَّجٌ.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>وغُلام جَخْدلٌ، وجُخْدُلٌ،<span class="c5"> كِلَاهُمَا:</span> حادِرٌ سَمين.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span><span class="c5">والمُجْلَخِدُّ:</span> المُسَتلقي الَّذِي قد رَمى بِنَفسِهِ،<span class="c5"> انشد يَعْقُوب لأعرابية تَهْجو زَوجها:</span><a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>إِذا جْلخد لم يَكَدْ يُراوِحُ هِلباجةٌ خَفَيْسَأً دُحَادِحُ<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>